# Workspace Layout

This workspace contains:

- **basestrike/** – Primary app. Base Mini App (Farcaster) tactical shooter. Next.js app at repo root: `app/`, `lib/`, `components/`, `minikit.config.ts`, `vercel.json`. Make this production-ready per AGENTS.md and production-checklist.mdc.
- **base-mini-app/** – Simpler Farcaster Mini App template (OnchainKit, no game). Improve only when relevant to basestrike or when explicitly requested.

When editing files under `basestrike/`, apply base-miniapp.mdc, game-phaser.mdc, and security-env.mdc as appropriate. When editing under `base-mini-app/`, apply typescript-next.mdc and base-miniapp conventions for manifest/auth only.
